[{"title":"SHCTF2024","url":"/2024/10/15/SHCTF2024/","content":"不会，太菜了，学吧：1.d_known这算是典型简单RSA加密问题？不晓得\n哦，对了，这题是动态flag\n然后这是题：\nfrom Crypto.Util.number import *from gmpy2 import*from flag import flagm = bytes_to_long(flag)p = getPrime(1024)q = next_prime(p)n = p * qe = 0x10001d = inverse(e, (p-1) * (q-1))c = pow(m, e, n)print(c)print(d)&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;c =  = &#x27;&#x27;&#x27;\n\n通过RSA加密：（那个公式块不会敲，你就假装有这东西吧），问ai了：$$ed≡1modφ(n)$$可以推出$$ed-1&#x3D;k*phi$$这个还是比较好推的\n然后我们知道了e（17和d（2048（官方wp给的是2046，应该是我算错了？但无伤大雅）以及phi的位数（2048，然后给k画个区间大概在（一会代码会写）一个区间，然后爆破：\nfrom Crypto.Util.number import *import gmpy2import sympyimport mathc =  =  = 65537kphi = e*d-1for i in range(2**13,2**17):    if kphi%i == 0:        phi = kphi//i        temp = gmpy2.iroot(phi,2)[0]        p = gmpy2.next_prime(temp)        q = sympy.prevprime(temp)        if d == inverse(e,(p-1)*(q-1)):            m = pow(c,d,p*q)            print(long_to_bytes(m))&#x27;bSHCTF&#123;f8d777b7-f736-4b72-9ae1-4d11a35dbe0e&#125;            \n\n","categories":["Crypto"],"tags":["Crypto"]},{"title":"Hello World","url":"/2025/06/01/hello-world/","content":"Welcome to Hexo! This is your very first post. Check documentation for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in troubleshooting or you can ask me on GitHub.\nQuick StartCreate a new post$ hexo new &quot;My New Post&quot;\n\nMore info: Writing\nRun server$ hexo server\n\nMore info: Server\nGenerate static files$ hexo generate\n\nMore info: Generating\nDeploy to remote sites$ hexo deploy\n\nMore info: Deployment\n","tags":["Crypto"]}]